<lyrics>[V1]
 1- fī saẙrika fī dẖī ạl̊ḥayāh̊
 saẘfa tarāka ạl̊jumūʿ̊
 ʿisẖ̊ ṭāhiraⁿạ rūḥaⁿạ jasad̊
 ḥatãy̱ yaraẘạ fīka yasūʿ̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: (hal̊ fīka yaraẘna yasūʿ̊)
   ạil̊haj̊ bihi daẘmaⁿạ kun̊ ʿab̊daⁿạ yaṭūʿ̊
   ḥatãy̱ yaraẘạ fīka yasūʿ̊

[V2]
 2- ḥayātuka ạảmāmahum̊
 sif̊ruⁿ kadẖāka ạl̊maṭ̊būʿ̊
 hal̊ lilsãmā taqūduhum̊
 hal̊ fīka yaraẘna yasūʿ̊?</lyrics>
<aka>fy syrk fy dẖy ạlḥyạẗ</aka>
<title>hl fyk yrwn yswʿ</title>
</song>